short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Type a paren, have it automatically close.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Now whenever you type a paren in webwork, the extension will automatically complete it. This extension also contains an experimental and buggy Wolfram|Alpha integration. You can click an equation and W|A will attempt to display it. Warning: don't rely too much on W|A.
